When working under `ops/`, this is the IWGF ops console (ops.iwgf.org) for Warp + Lattice. Warp callables live in `Warp12/functions`; Lattice panels should call the `lattice` functions codebase. Deploy stages through `Warp12/federation-hosting/ops`.

See root `AGENTS.md` and `ops/README.md`.
